%[text] # Getting Started with Array Product Toolbox
%[text] ## Description
%[text] This is a simple demo toolbox with some utilities that can demonstrate Array Product functionality.
%[text] ## Features
%[text] Provide an overview of the features that your toolbox integrates with MATLAB here.
%[text] ## Examples
in = [1,2,3];
out = arrayProduct(2,in);
plot(in, out); %[output:576886e6]
title("Array Product") %[output:576886e6]

